parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the automatic seat belt can cause the belt to malfunction, leading to inadequate restraint in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The seat belt fails to retract
gets stuck in the open position
does not buckle or release
causes discomfort or injury due to improper fit
and fails to provide adequate restraint in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt retractor can cause the seat belt to malfunction, leading to inadequate restraint in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The seat belt retractor fails to retract
gets stuck in the open position
does not buckle or release
and causes discomfort or injury due to improper fit.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the motorized shoulder belt can cause the belt to malfunction, leading to inadequate restraint in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The motorized shoulder belt fails to work
gets stuck in the open position
does not slide from front to back to secure the driver
and causes discomfort or injury due to improper fit.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Seat Belt System Failure in Accidents
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt system in accidents can cause inadequate restraint, leading to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The seat belt system fails to restrain the occupant during an accident
resulting in injuries or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door locks can cause the driver or passengers to become trapped inside the vehicle, which can lead to serious safety risks in emergency situations.
symptoms: The door locks fail to unlock or lock
the door handles do not open
the power door locks do not function
the doors become stuck in a locked or unlocked position
the doors cannot be opened from the inside or outside
and the driver or passengers may become trapped inside the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the automatic door locks can cause the doors to become stuck in a locked or unlocked position, which can lead to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The automatic door locks fail to lock or unlock
the doors become stuck in a locked or unlocked position
the doors cannot be opened from the inside or outside
and the driver or passengers may experience difficulty entering or exiting the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power door lock system can cause the doors to become stuck in a locked or unlocked position, which can lead to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The power door locks do not function
the doors become stuck in a locked or unlocked position
the doors cannot be opened from the inside or outside
and the driver or passengers may experience difficulty entering or exiting the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door hinges can cause the door to fall off, leading to potential injuries or accidents.
symptoms: The door falls off
the door hinges crack
the door is difficult to open
the door is unable to open
the door handle breaks away from the metal.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power door locks can cause occupants to be unable to enter or exit the vehicle, leading to potential safety hazards.
symptoms: The power door locks fail
the door locks are inoperable
the door locks rust
the door locks are unable to open from the inside or outside.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical door control unit can cause the door locks to fail, preventing occupants from entering or exiting the vehicle, leading to potential safety hazards.
symptoms: The electrical door relay is defective
the door lock solenoid fails
the door locks are inoperable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The throttle pedal sticking can cause sudden acceleration, loss of control, and accidents, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The throttle pedal feels stuck or hard to press
the pedal resists application
and then suddenly releases
causing the vehicle to lunge forward or accelerate unexpectedly. The pedal may stick in the up or down position
requiring excessive force to break loose.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cruise control system can cause sudden acceleration, loss of control, and accidents, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The cruise control system fails to function
causing the vehicle to accelerate unexpectedly or stick to the floor.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine stalling can cause loss of power, accidents, or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Vehicle stalls without warning
engine cuts off
engine vibration
engine failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Fuel system issues can cause engine stalling, loss of power, and accidents.
symptoms: Vehicle runs out of gas
fuel tank leakage
corrosion on the inside of the fuel tank
fuel fumes smell.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine component failure can cause engine stalling, loss of power, and accidents.
symptoms: Engine head gasket leakage
idler bearings failure
piston blow through the block
engine mount bent.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Exhaust system issues can cause noise, vibration, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: Muffler failure
muffler noise
exhaust leak.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Power loss can cause accidents, especially when driving uphill or in high-altitude areas.
symptoms: Vehicle loses considerable power when driving uphill or in high-altitude areas.
